author: Times Of India
title: What happens when you get Covid-19
description: The virus, SARS-Cov-2, which causes Covid-19, enters your body once you breathe it in — after someone nearby has either coughed or sneezed or you have touched a contaminated surface with your hands, which then have touched your face.
